''' Men-kâ-là-ngî ''' ({{IAST|bāṅlā}} / {{lang|bn|বাংলা}} fe̍t-chá {{IAST|bāṅālī}} / {{lang|bn|বাঙালী}}) su̍k-yî [[Yin-Êu Ngî-hì]][[Yin-thu - Yî-lóng Ngî-chhu̍k]] ke [[Yin-thu Ngâ-li-ôn Ngî-kî]], he [[Men-kâ-là koet]] fò [[Yin-thu]] [[Sî-men-kâ-là-pâng]] fò [[Thi̍t-lî-phú-là-pâng]] ke [[kôn-fông ngî-ngièn]], sṳ́-yung ngìn-khiéu yok 2 yi 2 chhiên van-ngìn, he Yin-thu - Yî-lóng Ngî-chhu̍k chhai [[Yin-thi-ngî]] chṳ̂-heu thi-ngi thai ngî-ngièn. Men-kâ-là-ngî sṳ́-yung chú-yeu fûn-pu yî Men-kâ-là koet fò Yin-thu Sî-men-kâ-là-pâng tén. Men-kâ-là-ngî he 1913-ngièn [[Nok-pi-ngì vùn-ho̍k chióng]] fe̍t-tet chá [[Yîn-su̍k Yin-thu]] ke [[lò pîn Tet là na̍p thi̍t thai kô ngì]] ke mû-ngî. 
